incommunicative.中释: 不爱说话的, 沉默寡言的
incommunicative.英释: tending not to communicate with others; taciturn

inconsequential.中释: 不合逻辑的, 不合理的

interchangeable.英释: things that are interchangeable can be used instead of each other

pulchritudinous.中释: 美貌的, 标致的(常用作诙谐的夸张词)

indemnification.中释: 保护, 保障, 补偿, 补偿物

conventionality.英释: the quality or characteristic of being conventional, esp in behaviour, thinking, etc

personification.英释: someone who is a perfect example of a quality because they have a lot of it
